What you need to know:

At Eldoret Golf Club, James Komen, the Junior Golf Foundation North Rift representative, carded 38 points to claim the top prize in the Eldoret Oncology Golf Day and lady golfer Jedidah Keitany was second on 35, one better than third placed Cyril Kitiwa, Livingstone Telel and Jeremiah Kayago.The nines went to Wilson Sugut on 21 and Hellen Yego with a score of 18 points.